Annotation Interface Cacheable

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR}) public @interface Cacheable
Indicates that the target method or constructor, when used to build a builder by AutoBuiltDocumentedBuilder.from(java.lang.reflect.Executable, Alias[]), will result in a cached DocumentedBuilder.
